OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy start then rain
OL,7,Fspreading eastwards through the
OL,8,Fevening. Cloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,9,Fovernight, becoming drier with clear
OL,10,Fspells towards dawn. Winds becoming
OL,11,Fstrong.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA mixed day with some bright
OL,14,Fand sunny spells but also blustery
OL,15,Fshowers feeding in from the west,
OL,16,Fshowers perhaps wintry at times. Best
OL,17,Fof the sunny spells in east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
