OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers early Saturday,
OL,7,Fthen rain and strong winds spreading
OL,8,Fnorth later, becoming very strong
OL,9,Fovernight. Blustery showers as winds
OL,10,Fease on Sunday. Dry with sunny spells
OL,11,FMonday.
